high_descs: Turn around completely and walk up to the white table in front of you.
Pick up the piece of lettuce.
Turn to your left and walk up to the sink.
Rinse off the lettuce in the sink.
Turn around completely and head to the trash bin on your right.
Place the lettuce in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a piece of clean lettuce in the trash bin.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the white table.
Pick up the green vegetable from the back of the table.
Take the vegetable and turn left and right to locate the sink.
Place the vegetable in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the vegetable.
Carry the vegetable and turn around. Take a few steps and then turn right to the trash can.
Place the vegetable in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a vegetable and then throw it away.

anns.task_desc: place a clean lettuce head in the bin
